.Dd $Mdocdate: June 26 2008 $
.Dt UMS 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ums
.Nd USB mouse support
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "ums*     at uhidev?"
.Cd "wsmouse* at ums? mux 0"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for USB mice.
Access to the mouse is through the
.Xr wscons 4
driver.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr uhidev 4 ,
.Xr usb 4 ,
.Xr wsmouse 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver
first appeared in
.Ox 2.8 .
